About Us




Founded in 1995, Black Diamond Capital Management, L.L.C. (Black Diamond) is a privately held alternative asset management firm.
With decades of combined experience in the credit, distressed debt and private equity markets, Black Diamond’s investment professionals manages approximately $8 billion in assets, across the company’s three lines of business: Control Distressed/Private Equity, Hedge Fund and CLO vehicles.
Black Diamond’s unique business model utilizes the strengths of its complementary lines of business to strategically capitalize on opportunities throughout the credit cycle. By managing multiple vehicles that focus on investing in debt securities and by having a consistent core approach to investing, Black Diamond has amassed a track record of delivering superior returns to its investors.
Black Diamond is dedicated to maintaining a rigorous credit analysis process that drives its disciplined approach to investing and asset growth. Over the course of its over twenty year history, Black Diamond has developed a consistent philosophy of investing in debt securities that offer both structural protection and substantial underlying assets. This philosophy enables the company to protect against downside risk, while capitalizing on both broad market and individual company volatility.

© 2016 Black Diamond Capital Management, LLC. All rights reserved.









