Values




Black Diamond is guided by five core values that shape the company’s culture and guide the way the business operates.
Intelligence:
We offer superior intellectual capital, investment experience and restructuring know-how.
Experience:
We have an extensive track record that shows consistent success in underwriting, trading, restructuring and managing performing, stressed and control distressed investments through multiple market cycles.
Focus:
We maintain a focus on disciplined investing in our areas of expertise, and successfully combine bottoms up credit analysis with an in-depth knowledge of the credit system.
Passion:
We are passionate about our investors and our investments and remain at all times focused on delivering superior returns.
Patience:
We have the patience and strategic fortitude to maintain a consistent focus on long-term investment returns and the sustainable growth of our company.

© 2016 Black Diamond Capital Management, LLC. All rights reserved.






