July 22, 2017 6:08 AM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Black Diamond Capital Management, L.L.C.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Black Diamond Capital Management, L.L.C. is a private equity firm specializing in distressed debt, mezzanine, and turnaround investments in middle market. The firm invests in the public and private equity; fixed income; and alternative markets across the globe, including North America. Black Diamond Capital Management, L.L.C. was founded in 1995 and is based in Greenwich, Connecticut with additional offices in Lake Forest, Illinois and London, United Kingdom.


